use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uwd1665703208513.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uwd1665703208513.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uwd1665703208513.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uwd1665703208513\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters an end tag.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__topic_d136985e1_d136986e1_d136987e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__p_d136988e1_d136989e1_d136990e1\">Use the following syntax if namespace has already been enabled, or if namespace support is not required:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104uwd1665703208513_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__codeblock_ztd_3qn_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ENDELEMENT\n  params\n     string Name: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; ENDELEMENT operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__topic_d136991e1_d136992e1_d136993e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__p_d136994e1_d136995e1_d136996e1\">Use the following syntax to enable namespace support:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104uwd1665703208513_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__codeblock_zwg_jqn_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ENDELEMENT\n  params\n     string Name: in\n     string QName: in\n     string URI: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; ENDELEMENT operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__section_whb_kqn_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255232e68\">Arguments</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__dl_xvx_pqn_hwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\">Compatiblity mode parameters</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>—name of the tag.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\">Namespace parameters</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__ul_z53_tqn_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>—unqualified tag name, which is the tag name without\n                        the prefix.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">QName</var>—fully-qualified tag name (that is, the tag name\n                        including the prefix).</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var>—namespace with which prefix was previously\n                        associated, either in the same tag or in an earlier tag for which the end\n                        tag has not yet been parsed.</li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__section_utd_vqn_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255232e118\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__p_d137009e1_d137010e1_d137011e1\">This operation is called by\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> for each end tag\n            encountered.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uwd1665703208513__p_d137012e1_d137013e1_d137014e1\">The values of the parameters are the same values\n            that were provided with the corresponding <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> invocation for\n            the corresponding start tag.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kch1665703202145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSE</a><p>Parses a specified XML stream.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttv1665703202809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSEFILE</a><p>Parses an XML document in the specified file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtr1665703208047.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>STARTELEMENT</a><p>Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532871\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532871\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ENDELEMENT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters an end tag. Use the following syntax if namespace has already been enabled, or if namespace support is not required: Explain this code operation ENDELEMENT params string Name: in endparams Implement your code here end; ENDELEMENT operation Copy Use the following syntax to enable namespace support: Explain this code operation ENDELEMENT params string Name: in string QName: in string URI: in endparams Implement your code here end; ENDELEMENT operation Copy Arguments Compatiblity mode parameters Name —name of the tag. Namespace parameters Name —unqualified tag name, which is the tag name without the prefix. QName —fully-qualified tag name (that is, the tag name including the prefix). URI —namespace with which prefix was previously associated, either in the same tag or in an earlier tag for which the end tag has not yet been parsed. Description This operation is called by PARSE and PARSEFILE for each end tag encountered. The values of the parameters are the same values that were provided with the corresponding STARTELEMENT invocation for the corresponding start tag. Related Links PARSE Parses a specified XML stream. PARSEFILE Parses an XML document in the specified file. STARTELEMENT Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}